The entropy is calculated as \( H = -\sum p_i \log_2 p_i \).  
For the given probabilities: \( -\left[2 \cdot \frac{1}{4} \log_2 \frac{1}{4} + 4 \cdot \frac{1}{8} \log_2 \frac{1}{8} \right] = -\left[2 \cdot \frac{1}{4} \cdot (-2) + 4 \cdot \frac{1}{8} \cdot (-3) \right] = 1 + 1.5 = 2.5 \) bits/message.  

